    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斯潘基的战舞》是一款节奏型3D平台游戏，灵感源自30年代卡通，并融入电子摇摆乐元素！踏入节拍之都，探索这座万物随音乐律动起舞的奇幻都市！帮助蝙蝠斯潘基抵达市长梅特罗诺姆的办公室，为你的蝙蝠耳朵重获宁静！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/1c8eb53a853c6ca335bead14bb3128d6.poster.avif?t=1770490703\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/1c8eb53a853c6ca335bead14bb3128d6.webm?t=1770490703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/1c8eb53a853c6ca335bead14bb3128d6.mp4?t=1770490703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随音乐律动而战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《斯潘基的战斗摇摆》</strong>中，整个世界都随着配乐的节奏律动。音乐不仅是背景音，更是<strong>大都市的节拍器</strong>。敌人随上行拍跃动，平台随上行拍跳跃，陷阱总在节拍中触发。唯一不合拍的叛逆者？<strong>斯潘基</strong>。摇摆、拍打、滑行——驾驭节奏，或将其击得粉碎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/e475e9a7f25c3e99b120caee277bb2e1.poster.avif?t=1770490703\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/e475e9a7f25c3e99b120caee277bb2e1.webm?t=1770490703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337560/extras/e475e9a7f25c3e99b120caee277bb2e1.mp4?t=1770490703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我们中的一员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了都市不息的喧嚣，<strong>蝙蝠斯潘基</strong>戴上<strong>巨型扬声器</strong>，决心让<strong>市长地铁侏儒</strong>永远闭嘴。将城市的声浪反噬其身：放大低音，在军鼓声中弹跳，在号角声中滑行，用<strong>蝙蝠声纳</strong>探秘。是时候开干啦！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>大都会城</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战傲慢的指挥官，穿越充满活力、手工绘制的街区，每个街区都有自己的节奏、守护者和需要掌握的技巧。沿途探索力量、学习新招式，并遇见一群古怪的明星追梦人。谁与你心意相通？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节奏驱动的平台：</strong>每个敌人与平台都随音乐律动：掌握节奏规律，<strong>驾驭全局</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电子摇摆乐原声带：</strong>动感十足的配乐让城市充满活力，让你忍不住跟着节奏打起拍子。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古卡通风格：</strong>生动鲜活的世界充满个性，角色表情丰富，造型灵感源自30年代。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节奏叛逆者：</strong>扮演斯潘基时，你可以随心所欲地配合节奏...或打破常规。打破时间规则，创造属于你的机会，用自己的方式让城市安静下来。</p></li></ul>",
